### LEXICON/PRONUNCIATION DICTIONARY
# To use for training ASR system WITHOUT vowel length contrast
Directory: lang_o3g_NoLengthContrast
File: lexicon.txt (lexicon)
Description: lexicon contains words and their respective pronunciation using SAMPA symbols. Built from the concatenation of Fal et al. [1] and Diouf [2] dictionaries (about 8,724 entries), plus unknown words automatically phonetized using a G2P model [3]. No length tag added so far.

[1] Fal, A., Santos, R., and Doneux, J. L. (1990). Dictionnaire wolof-français: suvii d'un index franais-wolof. Karthala.
[2] Diouf, J. L. (2003). Dictionnaire wolof-français et français-wolof. KARTHALA Editions
[3] https://github.com/AdolfVonKleist/Phonetisaurus
.
